            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%99%AB%E7%97%AB%E5%8F%91%E4%BD%9C%E5%89%8D%E6%88%96%E6%9C%89%E8%BF%99%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%81%E5%85%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%99%AB%E7%97%AB%E5%8F%91%E4%BD%9C%E5%89%8D%E6%88%96%E6%9C%89%E8%BF%99%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%81%E5%85%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#癫痫发作前或有这四大征兆#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】专家表示，出现这些情况可能是癫痫要发作了：①眼前闪金光或看到彩条；②产生腹气上升或恶心；③一边胳膊麻木或不舒服；④突然倒地等。熬夜真的会诱发癫痫吗？专家提示，癫痫发作的诱因包括睡眠剥夺、闪光刺激、饮酒或是情绪激动、刺激性事情、任意停药等。 <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E7%99%AB%E7%97%AB%E5%85%B3%E7%88%B1%E6%97%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#国际癫痫关爱日#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>   <a href="http://t.cn/A6pmZrrU" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
